  <brief_title>Reducing Driving Offenses of Adolescent Drinkers</brief_title>
  <acronym>ROAD</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Control Trial of the Effectiveness of of Group Motivational Counseling and an Emergency Department Experience in Reducing Risky Alcohol Use and Driving Behaviors.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Rhode Island Hospital</agency>
