  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the effectiveness of four group session of motivational counseling plus six
      hours of direct observations of the emergency department trauma services in comparison to
      four group session and six hours of community volunteering and also in comparison to four
      hours of education and 16 hours of community volunteering in reducing alcohol use and high
      risk driving behaviors and offenses among court referred 16-20 year old drivers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
